FBIS4-29331 "dreas117_n_94001" FBIS-EAS-94-117 Daily Report 17 Jun 1994 Vietnam DPRK Envoy Holds News Conference on Withdrawal DPRK Envoy Holds News Conference on Withdrawal BK1706071294 Hanoi VNA in English 0607 GMT 17 Jun 94 BK1706071294 Hanoi VNA English BFN [Text] Hanoi VNA June 17 -- Ambassador of the Democratic People's Republic of Korea Han Min-chol held here yesterday a press conference to introduce the DPRK Foreign Ministry's statement dated June 13 on the nuclear issue of his country. At the function, Ambassador Han Min-chol informed the participants of the DPRK's withdrawal from the International Atomic Energy Agency (IAEA) and affirmed that this issue can only be resolved properly through negotiations and consultation.
